snippet.title: Nebula Online Trailer
snippet.description:
Sci-Fi MMORPG with the only one world for all players, it doesn’t matter, from which platform you will enter it: Android, IOS, Mac, Windows, Windows Phone, Facebook, Steam. Choose one among three races, who are on the warpath for domination in space.
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
For more:
http://www.playnebula.com
https://www.facebook.com/playnebula
